The Well is a cute little tea shop/restaurant/lounge tucked away in North Oakland. They have a wonderful selection of teas and vegetarian dishes - I enjoyed the Pickled Burdock Congee and the Immuni-Tea for a late afternoon lunch. I highly recommend swinging by if you’re in the mood for a chill cup of tea and a bite to eat.
